# Getting started with Bitly

To use any of the above modules, you need to connect your Bitly account to Integromat. If you do not have a Bitly account yet, you can create one at [Bitly.com](https://bitly.com/).

## Connecting the Bitly service to Integromat

To connect your Bitly account to Integromat, follow the general instructions for [Connecting to services](https://support.integromat.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001990194.html#create-a-connection). After you click the **Continue** button, Integromat will redirect you to the Bitly website where you will be prompted to grant Integromat access to your account:

![alt text](https://integromat.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360009136814/file.png)

Here, allow access by clicking the **Allow** button. Afterwards, you will be redirected back to the Integromat administration page. Now, you can continue creating your scenario.
